name: 奎因·蒂特科姆
name_full: 奎因·蒂特科姆 Quinn Titcomb
introduction: Quinn is a tiny but mighty actress known for her powerhouse vocals and ability to hang with the big kids! She has a strong Theater background having completed 4 Broadway National tours as well as multiple film/tv credits including the upcoming 2023 feature film "Theater Camp" starring Ben Platt, Noah Galvin and Amy Sedaris in which she portrays the principal character Alice. Quinn is known for her maturity and positive attitude and she will most definitely make you smile.
